WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.680 --> 00:00:10.679
God knows the depths of the pain we suffer,

2
00:00:10.679 --> 00:00:15.280
And the distress and sickness we endure.

3
00:00:15.280 --> 00:00:22.480
Yet, our trust in Him will never be disappointed;

4
00:00:22.480 --> 00:00:33.040
Far be it from Him to let reaching hands return empty.

5
00:00:33.040 --> 00:00:39.000
My Lord, I have no one but You.

6
00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:46.120
I reach out my hands, hoping for Your grace.

7
00:00:46.120 --> 00:00:53.440
The Generous One never rejects a servant's plea,

8
00:00:53.440 --> 00:01:05.640
Nor does He withhold His gifts from those who hope.

9
00:01:05.640 --> 00:01:09.520
How often He has poured out His grace before we even ask,

10
00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:18.600
Giving and enriching out of pure, boundless generosity.

11
00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:24.000
God knows the depths of the pain we suffer,

12
00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:39.320
And the distress and sickness we endure.

13
00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:46.520
God knows the depths of the pain we suffer,
And the distress and sickness we endure.

14
